("3eabc723-406e-4675-a87c-79e4e064e731","Darkness","Darkness fills the targeted area, blocking line of sight.",3,2,1,"190f3767-c086-4dc6-92be-9b83e16f4705",NULL),
("3ececdbe-711d-40b2-b81f-befa21eb6dcc","Dispel Magic","Choose one creature, object, or magical effect within range. Any spell of power 5 or lower on the target ends. For each spell of power 6 or higher on the target, make an ability check using your spellcasting ability. The DC equals 10 + the spell\'s power. On a successful check, the spell ends.",11,6,2,"190f3767-c086-4dc6-92be-9b83e16f4705",NULL),
("3f1cf5d4-31bd-4b38-8072-972ca44cf46e","Panic","The target must use its turn to move as far away from you as it can, if able, and cowers if unable",5,3,1,"190f3767-c086-4dc6-92be-9b83e16f4705",NULL),
