("6bd7d4e0-ceea-4c18-932f-9a9cd1bde29b","Polymorph II","You transform into a magical beast with stats purchased from an array of 28 points. You can purchase 5s and 6es, a 5 costs 17 points and a 6 costs 23 points.  You retain your class features, and can speak, but you can’t cast spells.",7,4,2,"d1672bb2-a849-4e12-88e4-548c96ec88a7",NULL),
("6d5254ac-29f9-44cd-b3da-d615941fdd8b","Haste","All of the effected creature’s actions take {your proficiency mod} fewer ticks",9,5,2,"d1672bb2-a849-4e12-88e4-548c96ec88a7",NULL),
