("75b99520-fc2a-47c0-a14d-1ff9b3fbb63d","Summon III","You summon a magical beast with -2 INT, -2 CHA and 16 points to distribute amongst the remaining attributes. \nIt has Your Tier + CON Hit Points\nYou also choose two of the following benefits: \n* A fly, swim or climb speed \n* Proficiency in a skill \n* proficiency in an attack \n* martial weapon proficiency \n* medium armor proficiency ",5,3,1,"d1672bb2-a849-4e12-88e4-548c96ec88a7",NULL),
