("a010c3b6-90f0-48cd-ba2a-585096ff435d","Alter I","The target and everything it is wearing or carrying take on a new appearance. This new appearance may be up to one foot shorter or taller than the target’s true form, and must have the same basic arrangement of limbs.",1,3,1,"d1672bb2-a849-4e12-88e4-548c96ec88a7",NULL),
